    Class and Description
    com.launchdarkly.client.utils.CachingStoreWrapper
    Referencing this class directly is deprecated; it is now part of the implementation of PersistentDataStoreBuilder and will be made package-private starting in version 5.0.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EvaluationReason.Error
    This type will be removed in a future version. Use EvaluationReason.getKind() instead and check for the EvaluationReason.Kind.ERROR value.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EvaluationReason.Fallthrough
    This type will be removed in a future version. Use EvaluationReason.getKind() instead and check for the EvaluationReason.Kind.FALLTHROUGH value.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EvaluationReason.Off
    This type will be removed in a future version. Use EvaluationReason.getKind() instead and check for the EvaluationReason.Kind.OFF value.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EvaluationReason.PrerequisiteFailed
    This type will be removed in a future version. Use EvaluationReason.getKind() instead and check for the EvaluationReason.Kind.PREREQUISITE_FAILED value.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EvaluationReason.RuleMatch
    This type will be removed in a future version. Use EvaluationReason.getKind() instead and check for the EvaluationReason.Kind.RULE_MATCH value.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EvaluationReason.TargetMatch
    This type will be removed in a future version. Use EvaluationReason.getKind() instead and check for the EvaluationReason.Kind.TARGET_MATCH value.
    com.launchdarkly.client.EventProcessor.NullEventProcessor
    Use Components.noEvents().
    com.launchdarkly.client.FeatureStoreCacheConfig
    This has been superseded by the PersistentDataStoreBuilder interface.
    com.launchdarkly.client.files.FileComponents
    Use FileData.
    com.launchdarkly.client.files.FileDataSourceFactory 
    com.launchdarkly.client.RedisFeatureStore
    Use Redis.dataStore()
    com.launchdarkly.client.RedisFeatureStoreBuilder
    Use Redis.dataStore()
    com.launchdarkly.client.SegmentRule
    This class was made public in error and will be removed in a future release. It is used internally by the SDK.
    com.launchdarkly.client.TestFeatureStore
    Will be replaced by a file-based test fixture.
    com.launchdarkly.client.UpdateProcessor.NullUpdateProcessor
    Use Components.externalUpdatesOnly() instead of referring to this implementation class directly.

  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDConfig.Builder.allAttributesPrivate(boolean)
    Use Components.sendEvents() with EventProcessorBuilder.allAttributesPrivate(boolean).
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDClientInterface.allFlags(LDUser)
    Use LDClientInterface.allFlagsState(com.launchdarkly.client.LDUser, com.launchdarkly.client.FlagsStateOption...) instead. Current versions of the client-side SDK will not generate analytics events correctly if you pass the result of allFlags().
    com.launchdarkly.client.value.LDValue.asJsonElement()
    The Gson types may be removed from the public API at some point; it is preferable to use getters like LDValue.booleanValue() and LDValue.getType().
    com.launchdarkly.client.value.LDValue.asUnsafeJsonElement()
    This method will be removed in a future version. Application code should always use LDValue.asJsonElement().
    com.launchdarkly.client.RedisFeatureStoreBuilder.asyncRefresh(boolean)
    Use RedisFeatureStoreBuilder.caching(FeatureStoreCacheConfig) and FeatureStoreCacheConfig.staleValuesPolicy(com.launchdarkly.client.FeatureStoreCacheConfig.StaleValuesPolicy).
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDConfig.Builder.baseURI(URI)
    Use Components.streamingDataSource() with StreamingDataSourceBuilder.pollingBaseURI(URI), or Components.pollingDataSource() with PollingDataSourceBuilder.baseURI(URI).
    com.launchdarkly.client.RedisFeatureStoreBuilder.cacheTime(long, TimeUnit)
    use RedisFeatureStoreBuilder.caching(FeatureStoreCacheConfig) and FeatureStoreCacheConfig.ttl(long, TimeUnit).
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDConfig.Builder.capacity(int)
    Use Components.sendEvents() with EventProcessorBuilder.capacity(int).
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDConfig.Builder.connectTimeout(int)
    Use Components.httpConfiguration() with HttpConfigurationBuilder.connectTimeoutMillis(int).
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDConfig.Builder.connectTimeoutMillis(int)
    Use Components.httpConfiguration() with HttpConfigurationBuilder.connectTimeoutMillis(int).
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDUser.Builder.country(LDCountryCode)
    As of version 4.10.0. In the next major release the SDK will no longer include the LDCountryCode class. Applications should use LDUser.Builder.country(String) instead.
    com.launchdarkly.client.interfaces.PersistentDataStoreFactory.createPersistentDataStore()
    Do not reference this method directly, as the FeatureStoreCore interface will be replaced in 5.0.
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDUser.Builder.custom(String, JsonElement)
    Use LDUser.Builder.custom(String, LDValue).
    com.launchdarkly.client.Components.defaultEventProcessor()
    Use Components.sendEvents() or Components.noEvents().
    com.launchdarkly.client.Components.defaultUpdateProcessor()
    Use Components.streamingDataSource(), Components.pollingDataSource(), or Components.externalUpdatesOnly().
    com.launchdarkly.client.LDConfig.Builder.eventProcessorFactory(EventProcessorFactory)
    Use LDConfig.Builder.events(EventProcessorFactory).

    Use @link Components.sendEvents() wtih EventProcessorBuilder.baseURI(URI).

    Use Components.sendEvents() with EventProcessorBuilder.flushIntervalSeconds(int).

    The Gson types may be removed from the public API at some point; it is preferable to use factory methods like LDValue.of(boolean).

    Use Components.sendEvents() with EventProcessorBuilder.inlineUsersInEvents(boolean).

    Use Components.inMemoryDataStore().

    As of version 4.10.0. In the next major release the SDK will no longer include the LDCountryCode class. Applications should use LDUser.Builder.privateCountry(String) instead.

    Use LDUser.Builder.privateCustom(String, LDValue).
